data.name: lblExtraInfo.Text
data.value:
When you click Finish, LAWC will index the Wallpaper folder you have specified (if you chose one). Otherwise, right click on the Image or Folder and choose Add Folder.
You can change settings at any time by pressing the Settings button on the main window. From there you can enter the Advanced Settings, or by pressing the "A" button on the main window. In there, turn on "Show Help Balloons in Settings" to see more information on what each setting does.
